CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 13, 1958, pg. 17 reads: "Finch-Crunkleton Marriage Solemnized - Ivy Aleta Finch, daughter of Mrs. Beatrice Finch, and Donald Crunkleton, son of Mr. and Mrs. J.H. Crunkleton, became man and wife in a ceremony performed Nov. 29, in Holy Rosary R.C. Church. The Rev. Patrick J. Jones officiated."
TitMainTitle: Donald Crunkleton and Ivy Aleta Finch Crunkleton, cutting three tiered wedding cake, standing in front of window with venetian blind and geometric patterned curtains
